NOTE:  This DVD is the revised DVD from the one seeded a few weeks ago.  The video &quot;Origin of Life Made Easy&quot; has been revised to correct errors replaced.  This DVD is the current correct and working DVD.

Search Yahoo Groups for &quot;madeeasygroup&quot; for more information, and go to youtube and search for &quot;potholer54&quot;


